class FunctionSubstringIndex : public IFunction {
   Status execute_impl(FunctionContext* context, Block& block, const ColumnNumbers& arguments,

        for (size_t i = 1; i <= 2; i++) {

            if (!is_column_const(*columnPtr)) {

}
